description.en-us:
These iconic Star Wars ships are faithfully recreated by Hot Wheels. They include the finest details and even include a so-called 'Flight Navigator', this is basically a stand for the ship in which you can insert a finger and swoosh the spaceship around. In 2017 the 'Flight Navigator' was replaced by 'Flight Stand', a round base displaying faction logos.
All castings were designed by Chris Colangelo .
